until I get it done?

36:04.840 --> 36:06.285
All right.

36:18.320 --> 36:23.087
You know a place is haunted
when it feels more real than you are.

36:25.840 --> 36:30.767
It's like time doesn't pass,
it just layers over things.

36:31.440 --> 36:36.207
