the surface of what we see.

36:37.680 --> 36:38.681
You feel that?

36:42.200 --> 36:43.804
Well, you should.

36:44.760 --> 36:47.286
It's your family's blood
that got spilled here.

36:48.960 --> 36:52.487
It's what I told you,
South was never one thing,

36:53.680 --> 36:55.967
