42:14.440 --> 42:17.125
Yeah. Sure.

42:18.840 --> 42:19.841
Okay.

42:21.440 --> 42:23.329
I better get back to work.

42:23.760 --> 42:27.463
Better get out of here
before you get me fired.

42:27.920 --> 42:30.048
All right, well...

42:31.760 --> 42:32.807
- Okay.
- Okay.

42:37.600 --> 42:39.409
